txt.en: You have encountered Búrgoth, a cruel Orc Captain, driving his squad on a relentless search through the Dead Marshes.
A cruel Orc captain drives his squad ruthlessly across the marsh.
You have defeated the Orc Taskmaster Búrgoth and halted his relentless scouring of the Dead Marshes.
